143
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:25,670
He’ll be back soon, I guess.

144
00:08:29,200 --> 00:08:29,880
Wait.

145
00:08:30,390 --> 00:08:33,390
You just said there was no war
in the south?

146
00:08:33,390 --> 00:08:35,480
Hou Jian is dead?

147
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,640
What about His Majesty?

148
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,150
What about Governor Huang?

149
00:08:38,930 --> 00:08:40,440
Who is Hou Jian?

150
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:43,390
Who is Governor Huang?

151
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:45,470
I heard of him from the teacher.

152
00:08:45,470 --> 00:08:48,320
Hou Jian was a rebel
against the former dynasty.

153
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:51,240
But he’s been dead
for over twenty years.

154
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:53,440
Sir, is this the man you asked about?

155
00:08:54,450 --> 00:08:55,300
You’re dying.

156
00:08:55,300 --> 00:08:56,050
What the hell are you doing?

157
00:08:58,010 --> 00:08:59,100
You just said the former dynasty?

158
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:03,370
Hou Jian has been dead?

159
00:09:04,250 --> 00:09:07,690
Who is the emperor in the south now?

160
00:09:07,690 --> 00:09:10,450
Sir, what’s wrong with you?

161
00:09:10,450 --> 00:09:13,570
Emperor Xuan, of course.

162
00:09:13,570 --> 00:09:16,370
Who is that? What about His Majesty?

163
00:09:18,450 --> 00:09:20,690
What about Governor Huang Shenbian?

164
00:09:20,690 --> 00:09:22,690
Huang Shenbian?

165
00:09:23,370 --> 00:09:25,980
I heard of him from my uncle.

166
00:09:25,980 --> 00:09:28,930
But he’s also been dead
for over twenty years.

167
00:09:33,930 --> 00:09:36,660
Governor Huang fought hard

168
00:09:37,130 --> 00:09:38,930
and pledged to defend His Majesty.

169
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:41,610
