170
00:09:44,130 --> 00:09:45,780
The Xiao family is gone.

171
00:09:46,570 --> 00:09:48,050
His Majesty is gone.

172
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:54,780
That explains. That explains.

173
00:09:54,780 --> 00:09:57,930
