252
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:24,050
All right.

253
00:13:24,780 --> 00:13:26,980
After giving him some energy

254
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:28,100
and feeding him the decoction,

255
00:13:29,010 --> 00:13:32,450
we can finally keep him alive
for the moment.

256
00:13:43,780 --> 00:13:44,860
Tongming.

257
00:13:44,860 --> 00:13:46,660
