260
00:13:51,450 --> 00:13:53,010
<i>Chen Junfu, Immortal of Penglai</i>
You must be kidding.

261
00:13:53,010 --> 00:13:54,980
Even if you go personally,

262
00:13:54,980 --> 00:13:56,300
it’ll take more than one month
to get the Fire Lotus.

263
00:13:56,300 --> 00:13:58,300
Not to mention that young girl.

264
00:13:59,050 --> 00:14:00,340
I trust her.

265
00:14:00,930 --> 00:14:03,130
If she can’t come back in one month,

266
00:14:03,130 --> 00:14:04,130
